graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebook Workbench Images]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Notebooks -->|base images| UBI9[UBI9 Python 3.9<br/>registry.access.redhat.com]
    Notebooks -->|base images| UBI8[UBI8 Python 3.8<br/>registry.access.redhat.com]
    Notebooks -->|web IDE| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 3.6.x]
    Notebooks -->|notebook server| NotebookServer[Jupyter Notebook 6.5.x]
    Notebooks -->|CLI tools| OpenShiftCLI[OpenShift Client oc]
    Notebooks -->|data science| Pandas[Pandas 1.5.x]
    Notebooks -->|numerical| NumPy[NumPy 1.24.x]
    Notebooks -->|ML library| ScikitLearn[Scikit-learn 1.2.x]
    Notebooks -->|visualization| Matplotlib[Matplotlib 3.6.x]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - Framework Specific)
    Notebooks -.->|deep learning| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x]
    Notebooks -.->|deep learning| PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x]
    Notebooks -.->|GPU accel| CUDA[NVIDIA CUDA Toolkit<br/>11.8, 12.x]
    Notebooks -.->|Intel Gaudi| Habana[Intel Habana SynapseAI<br/>1.9-1.13]
    Notebooks -.->|Intel GPU| IntelOneAPI[Intel oneAPI]
    Notebooks -.->|AMD GPU| ROCm[AMD ROCm]
    Notebooks -.->|R IDE| RStudio[RStudio Server 4.3]
    Notebooks -.->|VS Code| CodeServer[code-server]
    Notebooks -.->|pipelines| Elyra[Elyra JupyterLab Extension]
    Notebooks -.->|explainability| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Toolkit]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|pod lifecycle| NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller]
    Notebooks -->|UI catalog| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    Notebooks -->|authentication| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar]
    Notebooks -->|image refs| ImageStreams[OpenShift ImageStreams]
    Notebooks -->|network access| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    Notebooks -->|storage| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaims]

    %% Integration Points
    NotebookController -->|creates pods| Notebooks
    Dashboard -->|displays images| Notebooks
    Dashboard -->|reads metadata| ImageStreams
    NotebookController -->|watches| ImageStreams

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    Notebooks -.->|image storage| Quay[Quay.io Registry]
    Notebooks -.->|package install| PyPI[PyPI Repository]
    Notebooks -.->|package install| CondaRepos[Conda Repositories]
    Notebooks -.->|git ops| GitHub[GitHub]
    Notebooks -.->|data access| S3[S3 / Object Storage]

    %% Build Infrastructure
    Notebooks -.->|build process| BuildConfig[OpenShift BuildConfig<br/>RStudio only]

